msgstr "当水位达到时泵<b>停止</b>"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:265
msgid "or bigger"
msgstr "或更大"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:266
msgid ""
"Pump <b>stop</b> if water level get closer to the sensor <b>blind "
"area</b> defined at sensor linked settings."
msgstr "如果水位接近传感器关联设置中定义的<b>盲区</b>，水泵将<b>停止</b>。"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:267
msgid ""
"Pump <b>stop</b> if the sensor is <b>offline</b> or controller lose "
"internet connection."
msgstr "如果传感器<b>离线</b>或控制器失去网络连接，水泵将<b>停止</b>。"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:269
msgid "This is an experimental feature; do not use it without supervision."
msgstr "这是实验性功能；请勿在无人监护的情况下使用。"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:270
msgid ""
"Ensure all necessary precautions are taken, as it may not work under your"
" specific conditions."
msgstr "请确保采取所有必要的预防措施，因为该功能在您的具体条件下可能无法正常工作。"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:271
msgid "Use Advanced Settings"
msgstr "使用高级设置"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:271
msgid ""
"to customize the smart mode for factors like water tank size, pump flow, "
"and other variables."
msgstr "以根据水箱大小、泵流量和其他变量自定义智能模式。"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:274
msgid ""
"Carefully read the <b>WiFi Water Level S1</b> sensor installation guide "
"before using this feature. Ensure the sensor inside the water tank is not"
" too close to the water inlet or floating valve and consistently provides"
" accurate water level readings."
msgstr "使用此功能前，请仔细阅读 <b>WiFi Water Level S1</b> 传感器安装指南。请确保水箱内的传感器不要过于靠近进水口或浮球阀，并持续提供准确的水位读数。"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:276
msgid "Open WiFi Water Level S1 Manual"
msgstr "打开 WiFi Water Level S1 手册"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:285
msgid "Smart Off"
msgstr "智能关闭"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:287
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    Enable the <b>smart off</b> conditions: <b>End "
"Level</b>, <b>Blind Area</b>, <b>Not Water Flow</b>, <b>Offline "
"Sensor</b>.<br>\n"
"                    If enabled, the pump will stop when the water level "
"reaches <b>End Level &#37;</b> or <b>Blind Area</b>,\n"
"                    if the linked sensor goes <b>offline</b>, or if no "
"incoming water flow is detected during the\n"
"                    <b>Flow Check</b> period.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    If <b>disabled</b>, the pump will <b>not stop</b> "
"automatically, and will require click the <b>ON/OFF</b> button at UI to "
"turn off the pump.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    <span class=\"badge text-bg-primary fw-bold\">Smart "
"Off</span> works independently of <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span>.\n"
"                    The <b>Blind Area</b> and <b>Offline Sensor</b> "
"conditions activate with <span class=\"badge text-bg-primary fw-"
"bold\">Smart Off</span>,\n"
"                    even if <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span> is disabled.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\">\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Don't Depends On: <span class=\"badge text-bg-"
"danger fw-bold\">Smart Mode</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\" >\n"
"                    启用 <b>Smart Off</b> "
"条件：<b>结束水位</b>、<b>盲区</b>、<b>无进水流</b>、<b>传感器离线</b>。<br>\n"
"                    启用后，当水位达到 <b>结束水位 &#37;</b> 或进入 <b>盲区</b> 时，水泵会停止；\n"
"                    若关联传感器 <b>离线</b>，或在 <b>流量检查</b> 周期内未检测到进水流量，\n"
"                    水泵也会停止。\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    若 <b>禁用</b>，水泵将<b>不会自动停止</b>，需要在 UI 中点击 <b>ON/OFF</b>"
" 按钮手动关闭。\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    <span class=\"badge text-bg-primary fw-bold\">Smart "
"Off</span> 可独立于 <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-bold\">Smart "
"Mode</span> 工作。\n"
"                    <b>盲区</b> 与 <b>传感器离线</b> 条件在启用 <span class=\"badge "
"text-bg-primary fw-bold\">Smart Off</span> 后生效，\n"
"                    即使 <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-bold\">Smart"
" Mode</span> 被禁用。\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\" >\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        不依赖于：<span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:312
msgid "Smart On"
msgstr "智能开启"

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:314
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\">\n"
"                    Enable the <b>smart on</b> condition: <b>Start "
"Level</b>.<br>\n"
"                    If enabled, the pump will start if water level "
"reaches or falls below <b>Start Level &#37;</b>.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    If <b>disabled</b>, the pump will <b>not start</b> "
"automatically, and will require click the <b>ON/OFF</b> button at UI to "
"turn on the pump.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\">\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        Requires: <span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 my-3\" >\n"
"                    启用 <b>Smart On</b> 条件：<b>启动水位</b>。<br>\n"
"                    启用后，当水位达到或低于 <b>启动水位 &#37;</b> 时，水泵会自动启动。\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p class=\"ms-4 alert alert-warning\" role=\"alert\">\n"
"                    若 <b>禁用</b>，水泵将<b>不会自动启动</b>，需要在 UI 中点击 <b>ON/OFF</b>"
" 按钮手动开启。\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\" >\n"
"                    <div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"                        依赖：<span class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-"
"bold\">Smart Mode</span>\n"
"                    </div>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"                "

