"\n"
"<p class=\"ms-4 my-3\" >\n"
"如果水位达到或低于此百分比，泵将启动。\n"
"</p>\n"
"<div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\" >\n"
"<div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"需要：<span class=\"badge text-bg-success fw-bold\">智能开启</span>和<span "
"class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-bold\">智能模式</span>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>\n"
"                "

#: templates/relay_device_info.html:344
