"</p>\n"
"<div class=\"row justify-content-md-center my-3\" >\n"
"<div class=\"col-md-auto my-2\">\n"
"需要：<span class=\"badge text-bg-primary fw-bold\">智能关闭</span>和<span "
"class=\"badge text-bg-danger fw-bold\">智能模式</span>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>\n"
