#: templates/products/r1.html:7
msgid ""
"Automatic Water Pump, water pump controller, smart water pump, energy-"
"saving water pump, water system integration, smart water systems, "
"automatic water control, S1 water pump"
msgstr "自动水泵、水泵控制器、智能水泵、节能水泵、水系统集成、智能水系统、自动水控、S1水泵"

#: templates/products/r1.html:17
msgid ""
"The Automatic Water Pump for S1 is a smart, energy-efficient solution for"
" automating water distribution. Ideal for home, agricultural, and "
"industrial water systems."
msgstr "S1 自动水泵是一种智能、节能的自动配水解决方案。非常适合家庭、农业和工业用水系统。"

#: templates/products/r1.html:130
msgid ""
"\n"
"            The <b>WiFi Smart Water Pump Controller S1</b> is a reliable "
"solution for managing water pump motors manually\n"
"            or automatically. Using data from the <b>"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<b>WiFi 智能水泵控制器 S1</b> 是手动管理水泵电机的可靠解决方案\n"
"或自动。使用 <b> 中的数据"

#: templates/products/r1.html:132
msgid ""
"sensor,\n"
"            it automates motor activation to optimize water and energy "
"usage. The controller starts the pump when the\n"
"            tank needs refilling based on its fill level and stops it "
"automatically once the tank is full.\n"
"            By improving efficiency, it helps reduce water waste and "
"electricity bills. Designed for ease of\n"
"            installation and maintenance, it’s an ideal choice for modern"
" water management.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"传感器，\n"
"它自动启动电机以优化水和能源的使用。当控制器启动泵时\n"
"水箱需要根据其液位进行加注，一旦水箱满了，就会自动停止。\n"
"通过提高效率，它有助于减少水浪费和电费。专为方便使用而设计\n"
"安装和维护方便，是现代水管理的理想选择。\n"
"            "

