#: templates/products/r1.html:154
msgid "Integration with S1 Sensor"
msgstr "与 S1 传感器集成"

#: templates/products/r1.html:160
msgid ""
"\n"
"            <p>Designed to seamlessly integrate with the <strong>WiFi "
"Water Level S1</strong>, the controller automatically\n"
"                receives real-time water level data and adjusts pump "
"operations for optimal water management. This ensures\n"
"                efficient automation without the need for manual "
"intervention.</p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<p>设计与<strong>WiFi水位S1</strong>无缝集成，控制器自动\n"
"接收实时水位数据并调整泵的运行以实现最佳的水管理。这确保了\n"
"高效自动化，无需人工干预。</p>\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/r1.html:167
msgid ""
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active\">\n"
"            <b>Automated Operation</b><br>\n"
"            <p>Equipped with advanced algorithms, the controller "
"automates pump operations based on water\n"
"                level sensor data. Users can configure thresholds and "
"parameters, dictating when the pump should activate\n"
"                or shut off, enhancing efficiency and minimizing manual "
"supervision.</p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"        <b>Customizable Settings</b><br>\n"
"            <p>Users can define precise thresholds for pump operation, "
"specifying when to start the pump if the\n"
"                water level falls below a set percentage and when to stop"
" it once the tank reaches a defined fill level.\n"
"                Additionally, scheduling and mode adjustments provide "
"flexibility to tailor the system to specific water\n"
"                management needs and conditions, ensuring optimal "
"performance and adaptability.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary active\">\n"
"            <b>No Incoming Flow Detection</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                As part of its automated operations, the pump can "
"automatically stop if no incoming water flow is detected.\n"
"                This feature is particularly useful for users relying on "
"unstable water sources to fill their tanks,\n"
"                helping to prevent unnecessary motor operation and "
"potential damage.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"            <b>Pump Compatibility</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Supports pumps rated for <b>AC 120V or 220V</b>, <b>50/60"
" Hz</b>, with <b>single-phase connection and neutral line</b>.\n"
"                Compatible with pumps up to a <b>maximum of 10 amps</b>. "
"Optional <b>ground connection</b> for added safety.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary active\">\n"
"            <b>External 2.4GHz WiFi Antenna (3dBi or 5dBi)</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Offers outdoor ranges of <b>100-150 meters</b> with a "
"<b>3dBi</b> antenna and up to <b>200 meters</b> with a <b>5dBi</b> "
"antenna, depending on line-of-sight.<br>\n"
"                Indoors, the range typically spans <b>30-70 meters</b>, "
"influenced by obstacles and antenna choice.\n"
"                Compatible with <b>2.4GHz WiFi</b> range extenders.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"        <b>Eco-Friendly Design</b><br>\n"
"        <p>The <strong>WiFi Smart Water Pump Controller S1</strong> "
"promotes sustainable water usage by reducing\n"
"            unnecessary pump operation. When paired with the solar-"
"powered <b>WiFi Water Level S1</b>,\n"
"            it creates an eco-friendly water management system that "
"conserves both water and energy.</p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active\">\n"
"            <b>Easy-to-Manufacture Design</b>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"               The energy module is integrated into a single PCB. The "
"sensor connects easily via a plug-in,\n"
"                with no soldering required when you purchase the pre-"
"assembled PCB, making it easy for anyone or\n"
"                any factory to manufacture in small batches.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-secondary\">\n"
"        <b>Open Hardware and Software</b><br>\n"
"        <p>With open hardware and software, the controller embraces "
"transparency and innovation.\n"
"            Users have access to its schematics, firmware, and software, "
"allowing for customization and\n"
"            future enhancements. It also integrates with a free version "
"of the cloud service\n"
"            for cost-effective data management.</p>\n"
"\n"
"            <div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9 video-wrapper my-2\">\n"
"              <video autoplay muted loop>\n"
"                <source src=\"https://github.com/rrguardo/WiFi-Smart-"
"Water-Pump-Controller-S1/raw/refs/heads/main/images/CShow1.mp4\" "
"type=\"video/mp4\">\n"
"                Your browser does not support the video tag.\n"
"              </video>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active\">\n"
"<b>自动化操作</b><br>\n"
"<p>配备先进的算法，控制器根据水自动进行泵操作\n"
"液位传感器数据。用户可以配置阈值和参数，规定泵何时启动\n"
"或关闭，提高效率并最大限度地减少人工监督。</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\" >\n"
"<b>可自定义设置</b><br>\n"
"<p>用户可以定义泵运行的精确阈值，指定在以下情况下何时启动泵：\n"
"水位低于设定百分比，以及一旦水箱达到定义的填充水位就何时停止。\n"
"此外，调度和模式调整提供了根据特定水定制系统的灵活性\n"
"管理需求和条件，确保最佳性能和适应性。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary active\">\n"
"<b>无传入流量检测</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"作为自动化操作的一部分，如果没有检测到进水，泵会自动停止。\n"
"此功能对于依赖不稳定水源来填充水箱的用户特别有用，\n"
"有助于防止不必要的电机操作和潜在的损坏。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\">\n"
"<b>泵兼容性</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"支持额定电压为 <b>AC 120V 或 220V</b>、<b>50/60 Hz</b> 的泵，具有 <b> 单相连接和中性线 </b>。\n"
"与最大 <b> 10 安培</b> 的泵兼容。可选 <b> 接地连接 </b> 以增加安全性。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary active\" >\n"
"<b>外部 2.4GHz WiFi 天线（3dBi 或 5dBi）</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"使用 <b>3dBi</b> 天线提供 <b>100-150 米</b> 的室外范围，使用 <b>5dBi</b> 天线提供长达 <b>200 "
"米</b>（具体取决于视距）。<br>\n"
"在室内，范围通常跨越 <b>30-70 米</b>，受障碍物和天线选择的影响。\n"
"与 <b>2.4GHz WiFi</b> 范围扩展器兼容。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\">\n"
"<b>环保设计</b><br>\n"
"<p><strong>WiFi 智能水泵控制器 S1</strong> 通过减少水量来促进可持续用水\n"
"不必要的泵操作。与太阳能<b>WiFi水位S1</b>配对时，\n"
"它创建了一个既节约水又节约能源的生态友好型水管理系统。</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active\" >\n"
"<b>易于制造的设计</b>\n"
"<p>\n"
"能源模块集成到单个 PCB 中。传感器通过插件轻松连接，\n"
"购买预组装 PCB 时无需焊接，任何人或任何人都可以轻松使用\n"
"任何工厂进行小批量生产。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"secondary\" >\n"
"<b>开放硬件和软件</b><br>\n"
"<p>凭借开放的硬件和软件，控制器具有透明度和创新性。\n"
"用户可以访问其原理图、固件和软件，从而可以进行定制和\n"
"未来的增强功能。它还集成了免费版本的云服务\n"
"用于经济高效的数据管理。</p>\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9 video-wrapper my-2\">\n"
"<video autoplay muted loop>\n"
"<source src=\"https://github.com/rrguardo/WiFi-Smart-Water-Pump-"
"Controller-S1/raw/refs/heads/main/images/CShow1.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">"
"\n"
"您的浏览器不支持视频标签。\n"
"</video>\n"
"</div>\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/s1.html:4 templates/products/s1.html:10
