msgstr "使用电池或交流电源运行。"

#: templates/products/s1.html:127
msgid ""
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active\">\n"
"            <b>Measures water levels in tanks with centimeter "
"precision</b><br>\n"
"            Obtain water level measurements of tanks or reservoirs on "
"your phone without needing to be near the device.\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"            <b>Wi-Fi Wireless Water Level Sensor</b><br>\n"
"\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Works wherever there is Wi-Fi internet coverage or where "
"it can be extended.\n"
"                This device uses your existing home Wi-Fi, allowing you "
"to check the water level from anywhere\n"
"                in the world as long as you have internet access.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active\">\n"
"<b>以厘米精度测量水箱中的水位</b><br>\n"
"无需靠近设备即可在手机上获取水箱或水库的水位测量值。\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\">\n"
"<b>Wi-Fi无线水位传感器</b><br>\n"
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"可以在有 Wi-Fi 互联网覆盖或可以扩展的地方工作。\n"
"该设备使用您现有的家庭 Wi-Fi，让您可以从任何地方检查水位\n"
"只要您能访问互联网，就可以在世界各地。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"        "

#: templates/products/s1.html:144
msgid ""
"\n"
"            <b>Eco-Friendly Solar Power Input with Battery Backup</b>\n"
"\n"
"            <br> Fully autonomous solar power input with AA NiMH "
"batteries for backup, designed for eco-friendly\n"
"            energy use in areas that receive at least 3 hours of direct "
"sunlight daily.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<b>带备用电池的环保太阳能输入</b>\n"
"\n"
"<br> 全自动太阳能电源输入，配有 AA 镍氢电池备用，专为环保而设计\n"
"每天至少接受 3 小时阳光直射的区域的能源使用情况。\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/s1.html:152
msgid ""
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"            <b>Water Level Alerts via Email or Web UI</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Receive notifications when the water level is above or "
"below a specified percentage or if the device goes offline.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active \">\n"
"            <b>USB-C Input Power  </b>\n"
"            <br> Flexible input power through a standard <b>USB-C</b> "
"connection.\n"
"            Perfect for indoor use or locations with limited or no "
"sunlight.\n"
"\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<Li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\">\n"
"<b>通过电子邮件或 Web UI 发出水位警报</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"当水位高于或低于指定百分比或设备离线时接收通知。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</Li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active \">\n"
"<b>USB-C 输入电源 </b>\n"
"<br> 通过标准 <b>USB-C</b> 连接灵活输入电源。\n"
"非常适合室内使用或阳光有限或没有阳光的地方。\n"
"\n"
"</li>\n"
"        "

#: templates/products/s1.html:167
msgid ""
"\n"
"            <b>Responsive Web App for Water Level Monitoring</b>\n"
"            <br>Monitor your water level from anywhere using your "
"cellphone, tablet, laptop, or PC.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<b>用于水位监测的响应式网络应用程序</b>\n"
"<br>使用手机、平板电脑、笔记本电脑或 PC 随时随地监控水位。\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/s1.html:176
msgid "View Live Demo Web App"
msgstr "查看现场演示 Web 应用程序"

#: templates/products/s1.html:180
msgid ""
"\n"
"            <b>Flexible Measurement Range from 2 cm to 8 meters</b>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                The measurement range depends on the sensor used. For the"
" most common waterproof <b>AJ-SR04M sensor</b>,\n"
"                the typical range is from <b>20 cm to 4 meters</b>, and "
"sometimes up to 8 meters.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<b>灵活的测量范围从 2 厘米到 8 米</b>\n"
"<p>\n"
"测量范围取决于所使用的传感器。对于最常见的防水<b>AJ-SR04M传感器</b>，\n"
"典型范围为 <b>20 厘米至 4 米</b>，有时可达 8 米。\n"
"</p>\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/s1.html:189
msgid ""
"\n"
"            <a href=\"https://oshwlab.com/rrguardo83/water-"
"level-.pro-s1-v2\" target=\"_blank\">\n"
"                Open Hardware and Open Source Code under GPL3, including "
"3D case models</a>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Users are free to produce, modify, or resell the hardware"
" and code in accordance with GPL3 terms.<br>\n"
"                Experience the future today by 3D printing the device "
"case at home and either ordering or\n"
"                assembling the electronics yourself.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<a href=\"https://oshwlab.com/rrguardo83/water-level-.pro-s1-v2\" "
"target=\"_blank\">\n"
"GPL3 下的开放硬件和开放源代码，包括 3D 案例模型</a>\n"
"<p>\n"
"用户可以根据 GPL3 条款自由生产、修改或转售硬件和代码。<br>\n"
"今天通过在家 3D 打印设备外壳并订购或体验未来\n"
"自己组装电子设备。\n"
"</p>\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/s1.html:212
msgid ""
"\n"
"            <b>Remote Web Administration of Device Parameters.<br>\n"
"                Access and adjust device settings conveniently from any "
"web browser.\n"
"            </b><br><br>\n"
"            <b>Available adjustment options include:</b>\n"
"            <ul class=\"list-group ms-3 list-group-numbered my-2\">\n"
"                <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-"
"group-item-info\">\n"
"                    <b>Empty Level:</b> Define the depth of the water "
"tank in centimeters. This measurement is taken from the sensor to the "
"bottom of the tank.\n"
"                </li>\n"
"                <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-"
"group-item-dark text-white\">\n"
"                    <b>Top Margin:</b>\n"
"                    Specify the margin in centimeters from the sensor to "
"the maximum water level of the tank.<br>\n"
"                    This setting is useful for tanks with a shut-off "
"valve that prevents overfilling by stopping at a specific distance below "
"the top cover.\n"
"                </li>\n"
"                <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-"
"group-item-info\">\n"
"                    <b>Water Level Measurement Frequency:</b><br>\n"
"                    Set how often water level measurements are taken.<br>"
"\n"
"                    This feature is useful for conserving battery life or"
" monitoring flow levels more quickly.\n"
"                </li>\n"
"            </ul>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<b>设备参数的远程 Web 管理.<br>\n"
"从任何网络浏览器方便地访问和调整设备设置。\n"
"</b><br><br>\n"
"<b>可用的调整选项包括：</b>\n"
"<ul class=\"list-group ms-3 list-group-numbered my-2\" >\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"info\">\n"
"<b>空水位：</b> 定义水箱的深度（以厘米为单位）。该测量是从传感器到水箱底部进行的。\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-dark "
"text-white\">\n"
"<b>上边距：</b>\n"
"指定从传感器到水箱最高水位的距离（以厘米为单位）。<br>\n"
"此设置对于带有截止阀的储罐非常有用，该截止阀通过停在顶盖下方特定距离处来防止溢出。\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"info\">\n"
"<b>水位测量频率：</b><br>\n"
"设置进行水位测量的频率。<br>\n"
"此功能对于延长电池寿命或更快地监控流量水平非常有用。\n"
"</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"            "

#: templates/products/s1.html:234
msgid ""
"\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active\">\n"
"            <b>Automatic Firmware Updates</b>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Keep your device up-to-date with the latest features and "
"improvements.\n"
"                Updates are applied automatically for a seamless user "
"experience.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"            <b>Designed and tested for outdoor and indoor use.</b><br>\n"
"            Built to withstand sun, rain, and wind under normal outdoor "
"conditions. Reliable performance indoors and outdoors alike.\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active\">\n"
"            <b>External 2.4GHz WiFi Antenna (3dBi or 5dBi)</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Offers outdoor ranges of <b>100-150 meters</b> with a "
"<b>3dBi</b> antenna and up to <b>200 meters</b> with a <b>5dBi</b> "
"antenna, depending on line-of-sight.<br>\n"
"                Indoors, the range typically spans <b>30-70 meters</b>, "
"influenced by obstacles and antenna choice.\n"
"                Compatible with <b>2.4GHz WiFi</b> range extenders.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"            <b>Low Energy Consumption</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Consumes approximately <b>75mA</b> while sending water "
"level data via <b>WiFi</b>.<br>\n"
"                In sleep/waiting mode, energy usage drops to just "
"<b>0.01mA</b>.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-success active\">\n"
"            <b>Easy-to-Manufacture Design</b>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"               The energy module is integrated into a single PCB. The "
"sensor connects easily via a plug-in,\n"
"                with no soldering required when you purchase the pre-"
"assembled PCB, making it easy for anyone or\n"
"                any factory to manufacture in small batches.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"        </li>\n"
"        <li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-"
"item-primary\">\n"
"           <b>Expected Operating Temperature Range</b><br>\n"
"            <p>\n"
"                Based on the components used, the expected temperature "
"range is from <b>-20°C (-4°F)</b> to <b>+50°C (122°F)</b>, although this "
"has not been tested extensively.\n"
"            </p>\n"
"         </li>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active\">\n"
"<b>自动固件更新</b>\n"
"<p>\n"
"让您的设备保持最新的最新功能和改进。\n"
"自动应用更新以获得无缝的用户体验。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\" >\n"
"<b>专为室外和室内使用而设计和测试。</b><br>\n"
"可在正常户外条件下承受日晒、雨淋和风吹。在室内和室外均具有可靠的性能。\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active\" >\n"
"<b>外部 2.4GHz WiFi 天线（3dBi 或 5dBi）</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"使用 <b>3dBi</b> 天线提供 <b>100-150 米</b> 的室外范围，使用 <b>5dBi</b> 天线提供长达 <b>200 "
"米</b>，具体取决于视距。<br>\n"
"在室内，范围通常跨越 <b>30-70 米</b>，受障碍物和天线选择的影响。\n"
"与 <b>2.4GHz WiFi</b> 范围扩展器兼容。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\" >\n"
"<b>低能耗</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"通过 <b>WiFi</b>.<br> 发送水位数据时消耗约 <b>75mA</b>\n"
"在睡眠/等待模式下，能耗降至仅为 <b>0.01mA</b>。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"success active\" >\n"
"<b>易于制造的设计</b>\n"
"<p>\n"
"能源模块集成到单个 PCB 中。传感器通过插件轻松连接，\n"
"购买预组装 PCB 时无需焊接，任何人或任何人都可以轻松使用\n"
"任何工厂进行小批量生产。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"<li class=\"list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-"
"primary\" >\n"
"<b>预期工作温度范围</b><br>\n"
"<p>\n"
"根据所使用的组件，预期温度范围为 <b>-20°C (-4°F)</b> 到 <b>+50°C (122°F)</b>，尽管尚未经过广泛测试。\n"
"</p>\n"
"</li>\n"
"        "

