msgid "To enable the smart automatic start and stop features, a <b>Water Level S1</b> sensor"
msgstr "要启用智能自动启停功能，需要一个 <b>Water Level S1</b> 传感器"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:386
msgid "Carefully read the"
msgstr "请仔细阅读"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:386
msgid "installation and usage manual for the <b>Water Level S1</b>"
msgstr "<b>Water Level S1</b> 的安装和使用手册"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:386
msgid "sensor and ensure it provides reliable and stable information under your specific conditions before activating the smart functions."
msgstr "传感器手册，并确保在启用智能功能之前，它在你的实际条件下能够提供稳定可靠的信息。"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:390
msgid "How Enable The Smart Features:"
msgstr "如何启用智能功能："

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:393
msgid "1) Log in"
msgstr "1) 登录"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:395
msgid "Log in to your"
msgstr "登录你的"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:395
msgid "account"
msgstr "账户"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:396
msgid "account using the same email address provided during the device's Wi-Fi setup. Ensure both emails match for proper account synchronization."
msgstr "账户，使用与设备 Wi-Fi 设置时提供的相同电子邮件地址。请确保两者一致以正确同步账户。"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:401
msgid "2) Enable the \"Smart Mode\" in Device Settings"
msgstr "2) 在设备设置中启用\"Smart Mode\""

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:403
msgid "After logging in, find your new device in the"
msgstr "登录后，在"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:403
