#: templates/manuals/r1.html:407
msgid "In the settings, enable the <b>\"Smart Mode\"</b>. All the settings are documented at <b>\"Device Settings\"</b> sections."
msgstr "在设置中，启用 <b>\"Smart Mode\"</b>。所有设置都在 <b>\"设备设置\"</b> 部分中有说明。"

#: templates/manuals/r1.html:415
